On 12/4/2012 4:52 PM, Mark L Hineline wrote:
> I don't care why people get into old VWs. If it's because they're kewl,
> that's okay with me. But I think it's helpful to know what motivated the
> brand success in the U.S, as well as the ethic that says - learn how to
